com.att.research.xacml.api

Interface Identifier

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SemanticString
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IdentifierImpl

    public interface Identifier
extends SemanticString
    Identifier is the interface for objects that represent a XACML 3.0 identifier. In most cases the IdentifierImpl in this package will suffice as an implementation of this interface, but all use of identifiers will use the Identifier interface to allow for extensions. Classes that implement the Identifier interface should override the equals method to meet the following semantics: Two Identifiers are equal if the values returned by the getUri method are equal.
    Version:
    $Revision: 1.2 $
    Author:
